item.dc:creator: @SEEPLUSPLUS SEEPLUSPLUS
item.description:
@SEEPLUSPLUS wrote:

[quote=“CoonHunter, post:7, topic:307195”][quote author=SEEPLUSPLUS link=topic=403323.msg3063285#msg3063285 date=1261011911]

Whys it helpful its just ints MAKE YOUR OWN?

Yeah, it has a lot of potential. Started making a GUI (for easy done easy go) That will auto rename should be done by tomorrow doing it the most horrid way possible though.

If you knew what you were talking about and were not so ignorant you could easily see that this can be made into a config that auto renames your client for you, or can help in de-renaming even. Even if you don’t know how to make the config just read the lines and replace.
[/quote]

Well thank you for bumping it, i posted this quite some time ago, and frankly, i had forgotten about it. Nice realizing exactly what you could do with it, but i do plan on making a auto-renaming tool for clients. So you can paste in code and hit “Rename” or “Un-Rename”, but that will mean creating an Int Database, so ill do 1 class at a time when i start on it.[/quote]
